{"tid":2508663,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"悲！IVA清盤 傳奇創辦人Charles de Vaulx自殺  生前堅持價值投資策略","createTime":"2021-04-29T02:28:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T05:37:38.000Z","uid":35519,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"61adb79b6e4cb2868e142aced7ffa904c98bdfd2","tid":2508663,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:28:22.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">悲！IVA清盤 傳奇創辦人Charles de Vaulx自殺<br />\n生前堅持價值投資策略</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nypost.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2021/04/de-vaulx.jpg?quality=80&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1200\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F2%2F2021%2F04%2Fde-vaulx.jpg%3Fquality%3D80%26strip%3Dall%26w%3D1200&h=198dbc98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名知名價值投資者在其金融帝國被宣告清盤後自殺，人們嘆息其為華爾街悲劇。<br />\n<br />\n據《紐約郵報》報導，警方透露，週一(26日)下午將近1點時，Charles de Vaulx進入了位於第五大道717號的中城豪華大廈，那裡一直是14年前成立的投資公司International Value Advisers (IVA)的辦公室。<br />\n<br />\n幾分鐘後，Charles de Vaulx從10樓墜下，現場急救人員於下午1點05分宣布他死亡。<br />\n<br />\n據大樓的一名員工說。Charles de Vaulx曾將IVA建成一家資產規模達到200億美元的金融巨頭，但上個月該公司突然面臨清盤。<br />\n<br />\n警方正在調查這位59歲的摩洛哥出生的金融家的死因，但沒有謀殺的嫌疑。Charles de Vaulx沒有被指控有任何不當行為。<br />\n<br />\n了解該公司的人士說，在對Charles de Vaulx離世原因進行考究時，這是這位才華橫溢的投資者的最後一次悲情行為，他的一生已經與其公司的命運緊密相連。<br />\n<br />\n一位不願透露姓名的知情人士告訴《紐約郵報》：「從很多方面來說，這都是莎士比亞式的悲劇&hellip;&hellip;具有諷刺意味的是，他持有的很多股票在過去幾個月裡都大幅升值了。」<br />\n<br />\n這位消息人士還說「Charles de Vaulx是個性格複雜的人，他很傲慢，覺得自己的價值投資使命失敗了，失去了存在的理由。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWWkePbZv5vNr6stUcUD8sUgZYrXgc54ByDgrSQqGLQWh?filename=ue4Pvss.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fue4Pvss.jpg&h=57994c5e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<em>▲ 左方為IVA創辦人Charles de Vaulx，右方為IVA前CIO Charles &rdquo;Chuck&rdquo; de Lardemelle</em><br />\n<br />\n一個月前，IVA在經歷了動蕩的一年之後進行了清盤程序。此外，Charles de Vaulx的長期合作夥伴、受人尊敬的基金經理Charles &rdquo;Chuck&rdquo; de Lardemelle也突然離職。<br />\n<br />\n由於IVA的價值投資策略&mdash;&mdash;買進估值過低的股票&mdash;&mdash;因疫情而受到打擊，反而成長型股票表現超卓，導致投資者紛紛撤資。<br />\n<br />\n儘管如此，清盤令一些投資者感到驚訝和困惑，因為Charles de Vaulx仍擁有一批忠實的客戶。<br />\n<br />\nIVA曾迅速成為美國增長最快的基金之一，但據知情人士透露，隨著時間過去，Charles de Vaulx和Chuck de Lardemelle在公司應該如何運營的問題上存在根本分歧，在哪些分析師應該向誰匯報以及如何組織工作流程等日常細節上爭論不休。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士稱，儘管IVA已成長為一家擁有約40名員工、受到華爾街密切關注的公司，Charles de Vaulx仍不願將任何控制權或責任讓與Chuck de Lardemelle。<br />\n<br />\n去年7月，Chuck de Lardemelle宣布離職，此舉令投資者感到失望，並結束了他與Charles de Vaulx的個人和職業關係。投資者認為，Chuck de Lardemelle的退出值得警惕。在接下來的六個月裡，隨著投資者撤資，該基金規模縮水至約30億美元。<br />\n<br />\n接近Charles de Vaulx的人士表示，儘管他身價數億美元，但一些投資者不再信任他，不再把自己的錢交給他，這對他來說是一個打擊。<br />\n<br />\nIVA網站上的一份聲明寫道：「我們懷著沉重的心情宣布董事長兼首席信息官Charles de Vaulx去世。在這個困難的時刻，整個IVA社區向他的家人表達了最深切的同情。」<br />\n<br />\nCharles de Vaulx留下了一個妻子和兩個孩子。"},{"pid":"a07a067120073864d7087e7c2ca22f2b849bfb00","tid":2508663,"uid":35519,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:31:00.000Z","msg":"順便估下渾水旗下Content Farm&mdash;Fortune Insight，<br />\n會唔會又去抄文賺click rate <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n定抑或借提出投資價值已死，宣傳自己乞會員呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQdyHdRZwKUfZReEkNockGcAhNronh6TbyG6pTB5ivWih?filename=4Ps5OpQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Ps5OpQ.png&h=9fa498e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e5de7cbab158df53043a9ace07bb3eb493dd70c","tid":2508663,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T04:37:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21f515b3f36bc99beee7ac922e0de86b31d77a96","tid":2508663,"uid":209890,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:07:36.000Z","msg":"gme爆煲之後華爾街將會遍佈廢老既屍體<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYKaGKWxeUUivuVhnSdJ3ngeDzNQBFCxA2PGuzrv993cA?filename=0Fm6yLt.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Fm6yLt.gif&h=e61012c0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dd1a79420528bbaf77960cc71eb3b94ff7959a41","tid":2508663,"uid":48294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:16:28.000Z","msg":"ark<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5df01a1862d79a8ef1d7fb896071f623ceb882a6","tid":2508663,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:21:58.000Z","msg":"呢間基金當年有揸一堆港股，成日扑中私有化<br />\n<br />\n<em>要數到今年投資表現好的高手，不得不提及International Value Advisers(IVA)，他們有披露股權的港股分別是亞太衛星(1045)、華地國際(1700)、白馬戶外媒體(100)及已除牌的亞洲衛星(1135)。後三者分別公布私有化或大股東計劃賣盤等消息，因而股價錄得不錯的升幅。</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/column/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93/%E4%BA%9E%E5%A4%AA%E8%A1%9B%E6%98%9F1045-198866\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fcolumn%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%2F%25E4%25BA%259E%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E8%25A1%259B%25E6%2598%259F1045-198866&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzfUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=d974391a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/column/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93/%E4%BA%9E%E5%A4%AA%E8%A1%9B%E6%98%9F1045-198866</a>"},{"pid":"a01a9f4d099278a4e1e8a15d7fb7f8dc4a8eed7d","tid":2508663,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21f515b3f36bc99beee7ac922e0de86b31d77a96","tid":2508663,"uid":209890,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:07:36.000Z","msg":"gme爆煲之後華爾街將會遍佈廢老既屍體<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Fm6yLt.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Fm6yLt.gif&h=e61012c0&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:29:37.000Z","msg":"求原圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37fae895a571e82f147ca724178e0d4ea6efbed0","tid":2508663,"uid":209890,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a01a9f4d099278a4e1e8a15d7fb7f8dc4a8eed7d","tid":2508663,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21f515b3f36bc99beee